File:Confederate National Flag since Mar 4 1865.svg|3rd National Flag<br>[never flown<ref>Sansing, David, [http://mshistorynow.mdah.state.ms.us/articles/107/history-of-the-confederate-flags|A Brief History of the Confederate Flags] at "Mississippi History Now" online Mississippi Historical Society. Third National Flag, "the bloodstained banner" references 19. Southern Historical Society Papers (cited hereafter as SHSP, volume number, date for the first entry, and page number), 24, 118. Section Heading "Second and Third National Flags". Retrieved 2012-10-04.</ref>]<br> "Blood Stained Banner"
